item.title: Different ips
item.dc:creator: @Epic_Steve Epic Steve
item.description:
@Epic_Steve wrote:

Start->CMD->“C:\WINDOWS\System32\ipconfig.exe”

IPv4 Address. . . . . . . . . . . : 192.168.#.# (Port forward with this)

http://whatsmyip.org/ -> “Your IP Address is …” (Use this IP to get users to connect - or use this ip to setup no-ip)
